text: The 1968 Navy Midshipmen football team represented the United States Naval Academy (USNA) during the 1968 NCAA University Division football season. Navy competed as an independent with no conference affiliation. The team was led by fourth-year head coach Bill Elias. ==Schedule== ==Roster== ==References== Navy Midshipmen Category:Navy Midshipmen football seasons Category:1968 in sports in Maryland
